Class Reservations

java.lang.Object
csc1035.project2.Reservations
@Entity(name="RESERVATIONS")
public class Reservations
extends java.lang.Object
Entity class representing Reservations. Contains 4 fields: The number of the room (room_number) The reservation date (res_date) The reservation time (res_time) The duration of the reservation (duration)
